                    ABA is...
                  </div>
                
                
                
                  <div class="commontext">
                    <p>the national trade association for independent booksellers &mdash; since 1900. ABA offers education, services and products, advocacy, and relevant business information. Look below for a selection of this month's key news and programs, or <a href="/files/open/pdf/membership/GenBro.pdf">see an overview of all ABA programs and benefits</a>.</p>
