<a href="http://www.bookweb.org/events/institute/wi6schedule/grid.html" target="_blank">Wi6 Fully Booked -- Waiting List Now Forming</a>


        
    </div>
  
  
    <img hspace="5" height="145" border="0" align="right" width="150" vspace="5" src="/index/middleColumnParagraphs/04/content_files/file/wi6logo.jpg" alt="" />ABA's <a href="http://www.bookweb.org/events/institute/wi6schedule/grid.html">Annual Winter Institute</a> -- scheduled for Washington, D.C., from January 19 - 21, 2011 -- is now fully booked.&nbsp;</p> <p>ABA members who would like to add their names to a waiting list for the event or for the host hotel <a href="mailto:kaitlin@bookweb.org, elizabethn@bookweb.org?subject=Wi6%20ABA%20Member%20Waiting%20List">should e-mail ABA's Member Relationship Managers</a>. As cancellations are received, spaces will be filled on a first-come, first-served basis.<br /> <br /> Booksellers who are registered can sign up now for the <a href="http://news.bookweb.org/news/wi6%E2%80%99s-indie-store-tour-limited-25-booksellers">Indie Store Tour</a> and make appointments for the <a href="http://news.bookweb.org/news/appointments-being-scheduled-now-wi6%E2%80%99s-consultation-station">Consultation Station</a>.</p>&nbsp;
  
  
    
      
      
      
    







