<div class="commontext rightColumnSection">
  
    <div class="sectionHeader">
      
          
            
            
          







<a href="/advocacy/health.html">Small Business Tax Credits for Health Care</a>


        
    </div>
  
  
  
    Qualifying small businesses can now receive a tax credit so that the cost of covering employee heath care is more affordable.</p>  <p><a href="http://www.bookweb.org/advocacy/health.html">Here's a lot more information</a> about how to know if your business qualifies and how to calculate your tax credit. And here's <a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2010/09/18/health/18patient.html">a <em>New York Times</em> story</a> about how the tax credit helped the Utah indie bookstore The King's English.</p>&nbsp;
  
  
</div>
